1
00:00:58,016 --> 00:01:00,992
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:00,992 --> 00:01:02,962
=Episode 23=

3
00:01:03,898 --> 00:01:06,938
(Play the Long Game)

4
00:01:06,938 --> 00:01:10,426
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

5
00:01:23,866 --> 00:01:27,537
♪Stroke by stroke, bit by bit♪

6
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:30,640
(Don't be afraid. I'll bring you home.)

7
00:01:31,879 --> 00:01:35,840
(If you have nowhere to go, why not
return with me and secure employment?)

8
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:37,760
What task?

9
00:01:38,719 --> 00:01:40,640
Be my husband.

10
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,599
(Since you already mirror him closely,)

11
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:48,879
I'll perfect your resemblance.

12
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:51,879
Why are you here?

13
00:01:52,799 --> 00:01:56,280
It's chilly at night,
so I brought you a cloak.

14
00:01:56,346 --> 00:01:59,641
♪Writing our unfinished story♪

15
00:02:00,319 --> 00:02:02,840
(It occurs to me
that you're much more likable)

16
00:02:03,319 --> 00:02:04,439
(when you're quiet.)

17
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:10,840
(Start by calling me "dear"?)

18
00:02:14,554 --> 00:02:20,319
♪This moment weaves eternity♪

19
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:21,280
Dear.

20
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:29,280
(A man, no matter
how gentle his nature,)

21
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,800
should protect his own wife.

22
00:02:31,866 --> 00:02:34,528
♪Like rain seeping into the earth♪

23
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,919
(Are you just using me)

24
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:39,280
and then throwing me away?

25
00:02:41,599 --> 00:02:44,199
(Honey, what more do you want?)

26
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,639
(Is this enough?)

27
00:02:46,842 --> 00:02:50,080
♪Helplessly falling for you♪

28
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:51,840
(Everyone has secrets.)

29
00:02:52,719 --> 00:02:54,360
(Regardless of our goals,)

30
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,080
we're allies for now.

31
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:02,120
(Best not to pry too deeply.)

32
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,719
Just go. Don't worry about me.

33
00:03:10,650 --> 00:03:13,973
♪Let time rush by♪

34
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,879
How could I leave you behind?

35
00:03:17,639 --> 00:03:19,479
(Don't worry. I'll be right back.)

36
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,280
Dear.

37
00:03:25,786 --> 00:03:32,439
♪A love poem awaits our rediscovery♪

38
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:33,759
Was I too heavy-handed?

39
00:03:34,879 --> 00:03:37,479
No, something just got in my eye.

40
00:03:38,919 --> 00:03:39,919
(Let me blow it out.)

41
00:03:47,482 --> 00:03:49,993
♪Carving a monument of longing♪

42
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:54,439
Spring Fever is the strongest love drug
at Zuixian Building.

43
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:56,680
Specifically used to tame resistant men.

44
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,759
What should be done then?

45
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,159
Beg me.

46
00:04:03,482 --> 00:04:07,137
♪I've failed you♪

47
00:04:08,737 --> 00:04:10,599
♪Pour this worldly brew♪

48
00:04:11,425 --> 00:04:13,255
♪I raise my cup♪

49
00:04:13,255 --> 00:04:17,691
♪Accompany you through ups and downs♪

50
00:04:18,817 --> 00:04:20,961
♪Tears of romance♪

51
00:04:21,351 --> 00:04:24,532
♪You smile so sadly♪

52
00:04:25,759 --> 00:04:28,480
(You should know this isn't compassion.)

53
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:31,240
(In this world of power,)

54
00:04:32,319 --> 00:04:33,600
(instead of killing someone,)

55
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:37,240
(why not turn them
into a blade in your hands?)

56
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,439
(It's clear the latter benefits more.)

57
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,560
(But...)

58
00:04:42,639 --> 00:04:44,680
(I'm nothing but a blade
in someone else's hands.)

59
00:04:45,210 --> 00:04:47,364
♪Drunk for you♪

60
00:04:47,639 --> 00:04:48,439
And you?

61
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,759
Have you ever truly cared for me?

62
00:04:56,186 --> 00:05:01,320
♪Our deep affection is an endless ode♪

63
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:04,154
♪Can't escape parting in this lifetime♪

64
00:05:04,154 --> 00:05:07,413
♪Meet again in the next life♪

65
00:05:09,279 --> 00:05:10,360
Don't leave.

66
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,360
I won't leave.

67
00:05:16,839 --> 00:05:18,439
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)
(You don't ask where I'm going?)

68
00:05:19,199 --> 00:05:23,759
No matter where you go,
I will wait here for your return.

69
00:05:25,530 --> 00:05:27,509
♪Tears of romance♪

70
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:30,839
(Who would've thought my frail husband)

71
00:05:31,279 --> 00:05:32,439
(possesses such skills?)

72
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:35,240
(Shouldn't you be resting?)

73
00:05:35,439 --> 00:05:38,079
Why the night stroll in black clothes?

74
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:40,160
Likewise.

75
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,319
Since you already know,

76
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:45,639
shall we work together from now on?

77
00:05:46,496 --> 00:05:48,397
♪This sorrow♪

78
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,079
Go...

79
00:05:51,834 --> 00:05:54,680
♪Drunk for you♪

80
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,480
And hurry back.

81
00:05:59,639 --> 00:06:00,759
May I kiss you?

82
00:06:01,839 --> 00:06:02,519
Dear.

83
00:06:02,842 --> 00:06:07,976
♪Our deep affection is an endless ode♪

84
00:06:08,186 --> 00:06:10,996
♪Can't escape parting in this lifetime♪

85
00:06:10,996 --> 00:06:14,409
♪Meet again in the next life♪

86
00:06:14,410 --> 00:06:18,949
♪Do you know my feelings♪

87
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,480
Qi and that Mr. Gu

88
00:06:38,639 --> 00:06:41,399
have been settled as you instructed.

89
00:06:43,079 --> 00:06:43,759
Understood.

90
00:06:44,839 --> 00:06:46,399
Do you have any other instructions?

91
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,839
You may leave.

92
00:06:48,439 --> 00:06:51,480
Should we clean up the wedding items
in the Fufeng Pavilion?

93
00:06:54,759 --> 00:06:55,279
No.

94
00:06:56,519 --> 00:06:59,000
Check when the next auspicious date is.

95
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,060
Yes.

96
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:26,639
Dear.

97
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,519
Do you truly refuse to believe me?

98
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,519
Very well.

99
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:05,079
Xuan Qing.

100
00:08:28,959 --> 00:08:29,600
Dear.

101
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:37,919
Is the bracelet I once meant
to give you still there?

102
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:41,879
What are your orders, Master Zhaoxi?

103
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:46,320
I never imagined
that after our brief separation,

104
00:08:46,759 --> 00:08:50,159
I'd return to find
everything so changed.

105
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,639
Master Zhaoxi, don't overthink it.

106
00:08:52,039 --> 00:08:55,759
I've arranged for a new auspicious date
to complete our wedding ceremony.

107
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,679
Now, I've become like this.

108
00:09:04,639 --> 00:09:06,320
Are you still willing to marry me?

109
00:09:07,159 --> 00:09:07,759
Of course.

110
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:14,399
Don't you want to marry me?

111
00:09:15,279 --> 00:09:15,879
Yes.

112
00:09:16,919 --> 00:09:17,840
I just...

113
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:23,519
Master Zhaoxi, don't worry.
Return and focus on recovering.

114
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:27,279
When we reset the auspicious date,
it will be time for our wedding.

115
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,399
Acting Master.

116
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,879
Did you see Mr. Gu Xuanwu?

117
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:36,799
No.

118
00:09:37,519 --> 00:09:40,039
Truly? Or do you refuse to mention him?

119
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,799
For the Pavilion Master position,

120
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,799
you challenged above your rank

121
00:09:45,039 --> 00:09:47,360
and even killed your newlywed husband.

122
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:50,679
Would you spare
Mr. Gu Xuanwu, your rival?

123
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:53,360
You truly stop at nothing.

124
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:55,759
You'd sacrifice your own comrades
to achieve your goals.

125
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,840
Stopping at nothing
to achieve one's aims.

126
00:09:58,919 --> 00:10:00,519
Isn't that what the Pavilion taught us?

127
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,960
You call me Acting Master.

128
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:07,759
Now, questioning me means
questioning the Pavilion itself.

129
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:13,240
My rise, my marriage.
They are my choices.

130
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:16,559
But have you ever chosen
anything for yourselves?

131
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:38,960
Have you heard?
The Young Madam is marrying again.

132
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,519
Because the family head promised

133
00:10:42,759 --> 00:10:45,720
to hand over the Xuanji Pavilion
to her only after the wedding.

134
00:10:46,679 --> 00:10:48,720
Does she desire the position
that desperately?

135
00:10:49,559 --> 00:10:52,799
Just days ago, I saw her
deeply affectionate with that man.

136
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,320
Who could've imagined she'd...?

137
00:10:54,759 --> 00:10:55,519
She's doing this

138
00:10:55,799 --> 00:10:58,080
just for the Pavilion
and the Gu family, isn't she?

139
00:10:58,279 --> 00:10:58,840
How dare you!

140
00:11:01,759 --> 00:11:03,879
Twenty strokes for both
and then kick them out.

141
00:11:04,399 --> 00:11:06,480
We don't need backbiting servants.

142
00:11:07,919 --> 00:11:10,360
- Spare us!
- Spare us!

143
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:12,759
Master.

144
00:11:13,159 --> 00:11:16,399
- Spare us!
- Spare us!

145
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,919
I hear you're picking a wedding date.

146
00:11:46,279 --> 00:11:47,720
Are you really going to...?

147
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:51,039
I was originally assigned
to Master Zhaoxi by the family head.

148
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:54,600
Now that he's returned,
the wedding must proceed.

149
00:11:56,039 --> 00:11:58,679
But the next auspicious date
is half a month away.

150
00:11:59,159 --> 00:12:00,120
You could...

151
00:12:03,399 --> 00:12:06,360
Three days have already passed.
I can't wait that long.

152
00:12:08,279 --> 00:12:09,639
Set it for three days from now.

153
00:12:10,399 --> 00:12:11,799
Why such urgency?

154
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:20,240
(When will the frost and snow return?)

155
00:12:22,039 --> 00:12:23,320
(May we meet again)

156
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,879
(when spirits return.)

157
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:36,480
Three days isn't enough
to remake a wedding gown.

158
00:12:37,919 --> 00:12:38,759
No need to remake it.

159
00:12:40,919 --> 00:12:43,080
But your wedding gown
is stained with blood.

160
00:12:44,399 --> 00:12:46,519
Just purchase any suitable set.

161
00:12:46,879 --> 00:12:48,039
Are you absolutely certain?

162
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:49,320
Of course.

163
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:52,600
Zhaoxi...

164
00:12:55,559 --> 00:12:57,960
I meant the groom you bowed with.

165
00:12:58,279 --> 00:12:58,840
He...

166
00:12:59,279 --> 00:13:00,200
I don't know.

167
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:28,320
(Some words, some things,)

168
00:13:28,879 --> 00:13:31,799
(once missed, bring endless regret.)

169
00:13:35,322 --> 00:13:41,210
(Xuanji Pavilion)

170
00:13:42,279 --> 00:13:43,360
Have you truly

171
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:46,200
made up your mind?

172
00:13:47,399 --> 00:13:48,080
Yes.

173
00:13:56,762 --> 00:13:59,578
(Pavilion Master's Token)

174
00:14:37,306 --> 00:14:43,226
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

175
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,360
Master Zhaoxi.

176
00:15:32,679 --> 00:15:33,879
Where are you going?

177
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:38,240
Why are you here?

178
00:15:41,799 --> 00:15:43,639
Master, Madam,

179
00:15:43,879 --> 00:15:45,039
why did you both go out?

180
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:47,399
On this joyous day,
don't miss the auspicious hour.

181
00:15:49,639 --> 00:15:52,519
I left the hairpin
Xuanji gave me in the room.

182
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:55,279
It's merely a hairpin.
Don't delay the moment.

183
00:15:57,399 --> 00:15:59,759
I noticed you'd forgotten the hairpin.

184
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:02,679
You go ahead. I'll get it now.

185
00:16:05,039 --> 00:16:07,240
Thank you, Master Zhaoxi.

186
00:16:29,818 --> 00:16:33,050
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

187
00:17:32,442 --> 00:17:35,872
(Combination lock)

188
00:17:36,602 --> 00:17:37,946
(Pavilion Master's Token)

189
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:57,559
Master Zhaoxi, the time has arrived.

190
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:02,519
This...

191
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:16,400
Master, I've succeeded and brought back

192
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:18,759
the Xuanji Pavilion Master's Token
as ordered.

193
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:20,799
Present it.

194
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:22,279
Yes.

195
00:18:28,602 --> 00:18:30,490
(Pavilion Master's Token)

196
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:34,319
Where is he?

197
00:18:35,119 --> 00:18:36,240
I'll go check immediately.

198
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:38,519
Master!

199
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:40,200
Master Zhaoxi has disappeared.

200
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:42,680
The room is a mess.
The secret compartment was opened.

201
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:44,119
The thing inside is gone.

202
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:45,640
You may leave.

203
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:46,599
Yes.

204
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:49,640
What was in the secret compartment?

205
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,119
The token.

206
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:02,720
The Xuanji Pavilion follows
the Master's Token, not the person.

207
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:06,640
Think carefully
about where the token is now.

208
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:08,960
No one blocks me today!

209
00:19:09,240 --> 00:19:11,519
When my master returns, you will die.

210
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:17,240
I withheld this earlier
to avoid disrupting everyone's plans.

211
00:19:18,519 --> 00:19:20,759
I'm uncertain if the one
who returned is Zhaoxi.

212
00:19:21,039 --> 00:19:23,640
But you are absolutely not Qi.

213
00:19:24,119 --> 00:19:26,319
Qi once confronted me over his pay.

214
00:19:27,519 --> 00:19:29,200
I wanted to whip him,

215
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:32,279
but I accidentally left
a scar behind his ear.

216
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,799
The other day, I happened to notice

217
00:19:38,759 --> 00:19:41,079
there was nothing behind your ear.

218
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:54,119
Allowing thieves to escape

219
00:19:55,039 --> 00:19:58,160
and bowing to whoever holds the token?

220
00:19:58,880 --> 00:20:01,640
Wouldn't that make
the Xuanji Pavilion a laughingstock?

221
00:20:03,319 --> 00:20:05,039
The winner takes all.

222
00:20:05,599 --> 00:20:07,000
Since the token has changed hands,

223
00:20:07,519 --> 00:20:11,359
whoever possesses it
commands the Pavilion.

224
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:14,960
Now, the token is in my master's hands.

225
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:17,799
Wise ones will step aside now!

226
00:20:22,039 --> 00:20:25,440
After Chief He's death,
I was rendered powerless.

227
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:27,480
You did very well.

228
00:20:28,119 --> 00:20:32,440
After taking the Xuanji Pavilion
and the Gu family, I need a manager.

229
00:20:33,160 --> 00:20:35,400
You will be...

230
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:40,240
No.

231
00:20:41,039 --> 00:20:42,240
Then what is this?

232
00:20:44,922 --> 00:20:45,946
(Pavilion Master's Token)

233
00:20:46,359 --> 00:20:49,559
What? Impossible!

234
00:20:50,799 --> 00:20:54,839
The token is forged from iron.
How could it be this light?

235
00:20:58,119 --> 00:20:59,119
I don't know.

236
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,079
You fool!

237
00:21:11,559 --> 00:21:14,799
Huan, I trust you've been well?

238
00:21:50,298 --> 00:21:55,361
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

239
00:21:55,642 --> 00:22:00,963
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

240
00:22:01,530 --> 00:22:08,158
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

241
00:22:08,158 --> 00:22:12,922
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

242
00:22:12,922 --> 00:22:15,258
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

243
00:22:15,258 --> 00:22:21,958
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

244
00:22:21,958 --> 00:22:28,730
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

245
00:22:28,730 --> 00:22:35,866
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

246
00:22:35,866 --> 00:22:40,250
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

247
00:22:40,250 --> 00:22:42,874
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

248
00:22:42,874 --> 00:22:49,508
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

249
00:22:49,508 --> 00:22:56,058
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

250
00:22:56,058 --> 00:23:03,182
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

251
00:23:03,272 --> 00:23:07,642
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

252
00:23:07,642 --> 00:23:10,350
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

253
00:23:10,350 --> 00:23:16,250
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

254
00:23:16,890 --> 00:23:22,878
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪
